text: Kabala may refer to: *Kabbalah, system of Jewish mysticism *Kabala, Sierra Leone, town in Sierra Leone *Kabala, Järva County, village in Türi Parish, Järva County, Estonia *Kabala, Rapla County, village in Rapla Parish, Rapla County, Estonia *Kabala, Mardin, town in Mardin Province of Turkey *Ka-Bala, 1967 fortune telling board game == See also == *Kavala, city in Greece, formerly sometimes transliterated Kabala *Cabala (disambiguation)
title: Kabala
